Description:
You arrive at an improvised elven camp and you stop to rest, but something doesn't seem right...

Suddenly the temperature drops even more and from the forest you see a pair of small red eyes appear...

When you realize you are surrounded.
DescriptionAction: You can feel it in your bones, it was a big mistake to stop here, now you can only hope to survive...
